  "lessons": {
    "s01": {
      "id": "s01",
      "problem": {
        "zh": "大模型只会输出文本。我们想要它能读写文件。差距在「循环」。",
        "en": "An LLM only emits text. We want it to read/write files. The missing piece is the loop."
      },
      "howItWorks": [
        {
          "title": {
            "zh": "不停地调用模型",
            "en": "Keep calling the model"
          },
          "desc": {
            "zh": "用 while(true) 包住模型调用。",
            "en": "Wrap the model call in while(true)."
          },
          "code": {
            "file": "src/loop.ts",
            "language": "ts",
            "snippet": "while (true) {\n  const response = await callModel({ systemPrompt, messages });",
            "highlightLines": [
              1,
              2
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "title": {
            "zh": "判断是否结束",
            "en": "Stop when no tools are called"
          },
          "desc": {
            "zh": "没有 tool_use 就返回。",
            "en": "If there's no tool_use, the loop returns."
          },
          "code": {
            "file": "src/loop.ts",
            "language": "ts",
            "snippet": "if (toolUses.length === 0) return response.content;",
            "highlightLines": [
              1
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "deepDive": {
        "zh": "这个模型↔工具的循环就是所有 agent 框架的本质。上下文即对话本身；长任务需压缩。",
        "en": "The model↔tools loop is the essence of every agent framework. Context is the conversation itself; long tasks need compaction."
      },
      "references": [
        {
          "title": "Building effective agents",
          "url": "https://www.anthropic.com/research/building-effective-agents"
        }
      ],
      "compare": {
        "rows": [
          {
            "label": {
              "zh": "停止条件",
              "en": "Stop condition"
            },
            "a": "runs until timeout",
            "b": "model stops itself"
          }
        ]
      },
      "loc": 16,
      "status": "ok"
    },
    "s02": {
      "id": "s02",
      "problem": {
        "zh": "同一个模型，表现不同——系统提示词在第一轮之前就定下基调。",
        "en": "Same model, different behavior — the system prompt sets the tone before turn one."
      },
      "howItWorks": [
        {
          "title": {
            "zh": "一段常量字符串",
            "en": "A constant string"
          },
          "desc": {
            "zh": "行为规则写成常量，注入 system 字段。",
            "en": "Rules as a constant, injected into the system field."
          },
          "code": {
            "file": "src/prompt.ts",
            "language": "ts",
            "snippet": "export const systemPrompt = \"You are nano-agent.\"; ",
            "highlightLines": [
              1
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "deepDive": {
        "zh": "系统提示词是 agent 的宪法；关键规则放在开头和结尾。",
        "en": "The system prompt is the agent's constitution; critical rules at start and end."
      },
